cs351.core

Interface Mutator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdaptiveHillClimbing, BasicHillClimbing, CrossMutateHillClimbing, HybridHillClimbing

    public interface Mutator
    A mutator should manage one Genome from generation to generation. It is up to the mutator to decide not only what type of mutation to perform on the genome, but which mutations should be favored in the future (ex: if a mutation is particularly successful).
